职位要求 Job Requirement：

1. 电子工程、通信类相关专业大专或本科学历 Associate or bachelor degree in Electronics Engineering, Communication Engineering or equivalent;	
2. 三年及以上EMC实验室测试工作经验 Minimum 3 years EMC Lab working experience as a tester;	
3. 熟悉使用和调试各类EMC实验室的测试仪器 Proficient skill in EMC Lab's instruments;	
4. 会熟悉使用WPS、Word、CAD等常规办公软件 Proficient skill in Office software;	
5. 基于某些项目进度要求，能接受合理的加班时间；有一定的抗压能力和坚定的执行力 Strong executive ability,able to work under stress and accept reasonable overtime hours;	

职位描述 Job Discription：

1. 协助整改工程师进行EMC摸底测试 EMC bottom-up testing;	
2. 根据摸底测试结果，整理摸底测试报告（包括测试数据记录及测试问题等）Output EMC testing report;	
3. 填写实验室温湿度记录、仪器设备使用记录 Fill in laboratory temperature and humidity records, as well as instrument and equipment usage records;	
4. 负责实验室设备日常维护与管理，设备的校准核查等 Responsible for daily maintenance and management of laboratory equipment, calibration and verification of equipment etc.	
5. 实验室的日常5S管理 Daily 5S management in the laboratory;
